"Stduent Management System"

//================================================
//	Requirments
//================================================
1- add new student
2- display all students
3- search for student by id
4- update student details
5- calc avg gpa
6- find max gpa
//================================================

//================================================
//  Windows
//================================================
1- Main:
	a- display main options:
		1- Add 		  2- displayAll 3- searchById 4- updateById
		5- deleteById 6- calcAvgGpa 7- getMaxGpa  8- Exit
	b- take user input

2- AddNewStudent:
	a- take user inputs:
		1- id 2- name 3- age 4- gpa
	b- go to main
	
3- DisplayAllStudents:
	a- display in organized way
	b- go to main
	 
4- SearchById:
	a- take id input
	b- show data if exits
	c- go to main
	
5- updateById:
	a- take id input
	b- ask for every input if want to change or not
	c- go to main

6- deleteById:
	a- take id input
	b- go to main
	
7- calcAvgGpa
	a- show avg gpa
	b- go to main
	
8- get max gpa student
	a- show max student gpa data
	b- go to main
//================================================


